title: 839. Kyler Murray, Top College QBs & Heisman Trophy Predictions with Joel Klatt
itunes:title: 839. Kyler Murray, Top College QBs & Heisman Trophy Predictions with Joel Klatt
description:
Daniel Jeremiah is back with a new episode of Move the Sticks and is joined by FOX Sports college football analyst Joel Klatt throughout the show. To start off, the guys look back at when quarterback Kyler Murray was in college at Oklahoma. Next, the pair break down a few of the top college quarterbacks in the country. To wrap up the show, the duo give their Heisman Trophy predictions and off the radar candidates as well.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
